  {
    "id": "f_csv_447505dbbd",
    "slug": "hit-don-t-make-no-difference-what-a-man-perfesses-i-been-in-a-heap-o-churches",
    "texto": "Hit don’t make no difference what a man perfesses. I been in a heap o’ churches. There’s the Nazarene Church and the Pentecost and the Holy Rollers and the Baptists and I don’t know what-all. I cain’t see much difference to nary one of ‘em. There’s a good to all of ‘em and there’s a bad.",
